			<common:generalComment xml:lang="en">Drilling is a cutting process where a drill bit is spun to cut a hole of circular cross-section in solid materials. The drill bit is usually a rotary cutting tool, often multi-point. Drilling operation is the first contact between the formation and the nonnative fluids and equipment. Drilling fluids play a vital role during the drilling operations. Drilling safety is a broad term that encompasses a variety of best practices and procedures designed to keep workers safe while operating drilling equipment.</common:generalComment>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="zh">钻孔是一种切割过程，其中钻头被旋转以在固体材料中切割出圆形横截面的孔。钻头通常是旋转切割工具，往往是多点的。钻孔操作是地层与非原生流体和设备之间的第一次接触。钻井液在钻孔操作中起着至关重要的作用。钻井安全是一个广泛的术语，包括各种最佳实践和程序，旨在在操作钻井设备时保障工人的安全。</common:generalComment>
